00:00:13.592 --> 00:00:19.293
Welcome to your favorite show Aha Emi Ruch!

00:00:28.641 --> 00:00:32.695
What are you going to cook for us today?
Kala Gulab Jamun

00:00:39.506 --> 00:00:42.372
Ingredients required for Kala Gulab Jamun

00:00:42.372 --> 00:00:50.981
Khoa, Maida Flour, Paneer, Sugar, Cardamom Powder, Cashew Nuts &amp; Oil

00:00:57.839 --> 00:01:08.796
First take a bowl add one cup of grated paneer into it

00:01:10.874 --> 00:01:17.845
Now add one cup of raw khoa in to the bowl

00:01:27.653 --> 00:01:34.998
Add one spoon of maida flour into the bowl

00:01:40.429 --> 00:01:46.680
Now add some milk into the bowl

00:01:50.313 --> 00:01:57.813
Mix them well to make a dough out of it

00:02:20.260 --> 00:02:31.647
Now make some small round shaped balls out of the dough

00:02:49.977 --> 00:02:55.483
Heat some oil in a pan for deep fry

00:03:24.762 --> 00:03:32.524
Deep fry the round shaped dough balls on low flame,
until they are golden brown in colour
