00:04:01,340 --&gt; 00:03:57,275
Remove the fried dough balls &amp; keep them aside

00:03:59.377 --> 00:04:06.599
Now heat some sugar syrup in a pan

00:04:40.299 --> 00:04:51.703
Add the fried dough balls into the sugar syrup &amp; let them soak for a while

00:05:01.314 --> 00:05:09.239
Now remove the soaked dough balls into serving bowl

00:05:10.629 --> 00:05:21.850
Add some sugar syrup into the bowl, top it with cashew nuts &amp; almond

